title: Jobs Pickup Should Give Fed Some Comfort: McKeown
description: Jennifer McKeown, Chief Global Economist at Capital Economics, looks ahead to the US jobs report and the outlook for rates with Bloomberg's Vonnie Quinn on 'Bloomberg Brief.' (Source: Bloomberg)
